### GET request to get all todos
#GET http://localhost:4000/api/todos


GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos?page=0&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc&search=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### USER should only see own todos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos?page=0&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

###

### USER should only see own todos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos?page=0&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{user_2_token}}

###

### USER own + shared todos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos/list?sort=createdAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

###

### Filter by category
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos?category=work&page=0&size=10&sort=title,asc
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

###

### Filter by tag
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos?tag=spring&page=0&size=10&sort=updatedAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

###

### Filter by category and tag
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos?category=work&tag=backend&page=0&size=10&sort=priority,asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Filter by completion status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos?completed=false&page=0&size=10&sort=dueDate,asc
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

###

### Combined filters
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos?category=work&tag=backend&completed=false&search=spring&page=0&size=10&
    sort=createdAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### LIST endpoint (without pagination)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos/list?sort=createdAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

###

### LIST endpoint with filters
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos/list?category=work&tag=backend&completed=false&search=cleanup&sort=priority,asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Show only archived
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos?archived=true&page=0&size=10&sort=updatedAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

